'49\t' + _x("npcprof", "Diplomat") + '\t500\t\t' + _x("npcprof", "Your party is considered to have the most beneficial arrangement of races in any social situation while %01 is in your party.  %01 takes %17 percent of all gold you find.") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "Not everyone knows how to talk strangers into giving them what they want.  I make it my specialty.  Bring me along and I'll use my skills to ease your way through society.  My rate is 500 gold to start and %17 percent of the gold we find.") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "Wait!  Let's talk about this!  I know you don't really want to dismiss me.  We can work it out!") + '\r\n'
