'51\t' + _x("npcprof", "Burglar") + '\t2000\t\t' + _x("npcprof", "Disarm Traps and Stealing skills are increased by eight points for each character and Reputation is decreased by one full category.  %01 costs you nothing!") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "Need traps disarmed?  Perhaps something retrieved without the owner's knowledge or consent?  I've been doing it ever since I was released from jail three years ago.  If you need help, I'll come with you for free!  I need the practice.  ") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "What?  I didn't do nothin!  ") + '\r\n'
