'53\t' + _x("npcprof", "Acolyte") + '\t500\t\t' + _x("npcprof", "Two point bonus to Self (body, mind, spirit) spell skills for all characters.  %01 takes %17 percent of all gold you find.") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "I can assist your spell casting by slightly boosting your spells of the Self for 500 gold to start and %17 percent of the gold we find..") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "By firing me, you're not just losing a friend and spiritual advisor, but your link to the Gods!  I know you don't really mean it.  You won't dismiss me.") + '\r\n'
