'56\t' + _x("npcprof", "Monk") + '\t500\t\t' + _x("npcprof", "Increases the unarmed and dodging skills by two for all characters.  %01 takes %17 percent of all gold you find.") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "I can help train your minds and bodies to perfect your unarmored, unarmed combat techniques.  I only require 500 gold to start and %17 percent of the gold we find.") + '\t' + _x("npcprof", "You, uh, haven't snatched the pebble from my hand yet, grasshopper.  Will you cut short your training so casually?") + '\r\n'
